        <item>
            <title>Tesla Optimus 机器人升级了新的手臂，轻松一手接好抛过来的球</title>
            <description>&lt;figure class=&quot;caas-figure&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;caas-figure-with-pb&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;caas-img-container&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;caas-img has-preview&quot; alt=&quot;Tesla Optimus&quot; src=&quot;https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-12/800b59b0-9a76-11ee-bbee-61ba9c1d3d5f&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;caption-wrapper caption-aligned-with-image&quot;&gt;&lt;figcaption class=&quot;caption-collapse&quot;&gt;Tesla &lt;a class=&quot;link &quot; href=&quot;https://tw.news.yahoo.com/tag/Optimus&quot; data-i13n=&quot;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:Optimus;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0&quot;&gt;Optimus&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;不知道大家在 Black Friday 黑色星期五入手什么心水好物呢？还未的话可以看看我们&lt;a data-i13n=&quot;cpos:1;pos:1&quot; href=&quot;https://hk.news.yahoo.com/live/black-friday-cyber-monday-2024-master-055744941.html&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:为大家准备的优惠合集;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;&quot; class=&quot;link  yahoo-link&quot;&gt;为大家准备的优惠合集&lt;/a&gt;。至于 Tesla 的 Optimus 机器人就在黑色星期五获得了一件「礼物」－更新款的手臂。升级新手臂后活动的范围大大增加，令 Optimus 机器人可以轻松做出接球的动作，或许可以考虑进军大联盟做外野手。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;twitter-tweet-wrapper&quot; data-embed-anchor=&quot;69a44a2b-bebc-5129-bcc8-d6f5838a5cd6&quot;&gt;&lt;blockquote placeholder=&quot;&quot; data-theme=&quot;light&quot; class=&quot;twitter-tweet&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;caas-card-loader small fixed-height&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Got a new hand for Black Friday &lt;a href=&quot;https://t.co/x3gQrsbYAQ&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:pic.twitter.com/x3gQrsbYAQ;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas&quot; class=&quot;link &quot;&gt;pic.twitter.com/x3gQrsbYAQ&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;— Tesla Optimus (@Tesla_Optimus) &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/Tesla_Optimus/status/1862116407594377698?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:November 28, 2024;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas&quot; class=&quot;link &quot;&gt;November 28, 2024&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;近日 Tesla Optimus 机器人就于其 X 帐户上&lt;a data-i13n=&quot;cpos:2;pos:1&quot; href=&quot;https://x.com/Tesla_Optimus/status/1862116407594377698&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:发布了一条影片;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas&quot; class=&quot;link &quot;&gt;发布了一条影片&lt;/a&gt;，表示它「在黑色星期五有新手臂使用了」。片中可见 Optimus 机器人轻松接著向它抛向的网球， Optimus 机器人的工程师 Milan Kovac 亦&lt;a data-i13n=&quot;cpos:3;pos:1&quot; href=&quot;https://x.com/_milankovac_/status/1862167219649818816&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:在 X 上发文;cpos:3;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas&quot; class=&quot;link &quot;&gt;在 X 上发文&lt;/a&gt;，表示新手臂加上新手掌后，Optimus 机器人现在拥有 22 个自由度（Degrees of Freedom，DoFs），手腕和前臂亦有三个，令 Optimus 机器人有更好的手部控制。不过他也补充这次接球示范是以遥控操作达成的，怪不得动作十分像真正的人类（毕竟是人去操作嘛），但亦可见其电机设计可容许做出如流畅而且细腻的动作是相当强劲。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;twitter-tweet-wrapper&quot; data-embed-anchor=&quot;c87a6b0a-ead0-571b-9599-2cbed43da358&quot;&gt;&lt;blockquote placeholder=&quot;&quot; data-theme=&quot;light&quot; class=&quot;twitter-tweet&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;caas-card-loader small fixed-height&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Our new hand/forearm with double the number of degrees of freedom now in action on the bot! There’s 22 DoFs on the hand, and 3 on the wrist/forearm. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;This little video was made last night in the lab (teleoperated) and is real-time. Gives us confidence that we’ll very soon be… &lt;a href=&quot;https://t.co/647FWdtkm7&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:https://t.co/647FWdtkm7;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas&quot; class=&quot;link &quot;&gt;https://t.co/647FWdtkm7&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;— Milan Kovac (@_milankovac_) &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/_milankovac_/status/1862167219649818816?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:November 28, 2024;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas&quot; class=&quot;link &quot;&gt;November 28, 2024&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;caas-da&quot;&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;sda-INARTICLE&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Milan Kovac 再指未来要为 Optimus 机器人加入</description>
